			Profile
			
			AprofessorattheDepartmentofOpticalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou,China,&nbsp;alsothepresidentofSENSINGInstrumentsCo.,Ltd.
HasbeenworkingonLightingandDisplaymetrologyover20years,withfocusonphotometry,colorimetry,andphotobiologicalsafetymetrologyoflightsources.
TherepresentativeofChinaintheIECworkinggroupTC76/WG9forOpticalRadiationSafetyofnon-laserSources.
TheprojectleaderofIEC62341-6-3forOLEDMeasuringMethodsofImageQualityandIEC62471-4forPhotobiologicalSafetyofLampsandLampSystems:MeasuringMethods.
ReceivedtheIEC1906Awardformy&nbsp;contributiontotheIEC.
AlsoamemberoftheIECworkinggroupTC110/WG5forOrganicLightEmittingDiodeDisplays,IECTC110/WG2forLiquidCrystalDisplaysandIECTC110/PT62595forBackLightUnit.
AmemberofICDM,andofChinaNationalStandardizationonOpticalRadiationSafety,LightingSourcesandLuminaires,LightingLED,FlatPanelDisplay,alsoa&nbsp;memberintheCIEDivision2andDivision6.
ChairmanofCIETC2-73forPhotobiologicalSafetyMeasurementofLightingProducts,andtheliaisonofCIEDivision2andIECTC110/WG5.
BeinchargeofdevelopmentofChinanationalstandardonassessmentofLEDradiationSafety,andmeasurementofLEDmodulesandFPDs.HeisthedirectorofChinaIlluminatingEngineeringSocietyandChinaAssociationofLightingIndustry,andadviserofChinaOpticsandOptoelectronicsManufacturesAssociationLEDDivision.
WonChinaGovernmentScienceAwardsformyachievementinmirrorgoniophotometersin2007,andwonfourconsecutiveawardsofChinaLEDInnovationTechnologyin2008,2009,2010and2011.
			
				
